r backs upon you [in flight], and will not be succoured.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/404.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":74421,"position":1,"arabic":"لَن","translation":"কক্ষণ না","audioUrl":"wbw/003_111_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74422,"position":2,"arabic":"يَضُرُّوكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদেরকে ক্ষতি করতে পারবে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_111_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74423,"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَّآ","translation":"এছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/003_111_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74424,"position":4,"arabic":"أَذًۭى ۖ","translation":"কষ্ট দেওয়া","audioUrl":"wbw/003_111_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74426,"position":5,"arabic":"وَإِن","translation":"আর যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/003_111_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74427,"position":6,"arabic":"يُقَـٰتِلُوكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের সাথে লড়ে তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_111_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74428,"position":7,"arabic":"يُوَلُّوكُمُ","translation":"তোমাদের দিকে ফিরাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_111_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74429,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْأَدْبَارَ","translation":"পিঠসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_111_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74430,"position":9,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_111_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74431,"position":10,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/003_111_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74432,"position":11,"arabic":"يُنصَرُونَ","translation":"তাদের সাহায্যও করা হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_111_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74433,"position":12,"arabic":"١١١","translation":"(১১১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":112,"arabic":"ضُرِبَتْ عَلَيْهِمُ ٱلذِّلَّةُ أَيْنَ مَا ثُقِفُوٓا۟ إِلَّا بِحَبْلٍۢ مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ وَحَبْلٍۢ مِّنَ ٱلنَّاسِ وَبَآءُو بِغَضَبٍۢ مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ وَضُرِبَتْ عَلَيْهِمُ ٱلْمَسْكَنَةُ ۚ ذَٰلِكَ بِأَنَّهُمْ كَانُوا۟ يَكْفُرُونَ بِـَٔايَٰتِ ٱللَّهِ وَيَقْتُلُونَ ٱلْأَنۢبِيَآءَ بِغَيْرِ حَقٍّۢ ۚ ذَٰلِكَ بِمَا عَصَوا۟ وَّكَانُوا۟ يَعْتَدُونَ","translation":"Overshadowed by ignominy are they wherever they may be, save [when they bind themselves again] in a bond with God and a bond with men; for they have earned the burden of God's condemnation, and are overshadowed by humiliation: all this [has befallen them] because they persisted in denying the truth of God's messages and in slaying the prophets against all right: all this, because they rebelled [against God], and persisted in transgressing the bounds of what is right.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/405.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":74620,"position":1,"arabic":"ضُرِبَتْ","translation":"মার পড়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_112_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74621,"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمُ","translation":"তাদের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_112_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74622,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلذِّلَّةُ","translation":"লাঞ্ছনা ও অপমানের","audioUrl":"wbw/003_112_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74623,"position":4,"arabic":"أَيْنَ","translation":"যেখানেই","audioUrl":"wbw/003_112_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74624,"position":5,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"(কি)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_112_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74625,"position":6,"arabic":"ثُقِفُوٓا۟","translation":"তাদের পাওয়া গিয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_112_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74626,"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"তবে এছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/003_112_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74627,"position":8,"arabic":"بِحَبْلٍۢ","translation":"আশ্রয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_112_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74628,"position":9,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"পক্ষ হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_112_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74629,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_112_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74630,"position":11,"arabic":"وَحَبْلٍۢ","translation":"অথবা আশ্রয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_112_